  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation results from bench-top pump loop experiments are included; hemolysis index predictions are compared against measured plasma-free haemoglobin values at five flow-speed operating points. Results indicate acceptable agreement at the assessed credibility level. Decision: Accepted at Low assurance.",
