    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps, the assessment team accepted the package at Low assurance level for the purpose of early-stage regulatory pre-submission. All seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels, and six factors remain unassessed epistemic gaps. The team notes that validation results at five operating points demonstrate hemolysis index predictions within 28% of measured values, which is considered acceptable for Low assurance. Full credibility remediation is required before pivotal submission.",
